38
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,920
Do you think as a father,

39
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,200
you deserve that title?

40
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,360
My dear father.

41
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:21,560
I won't let you and Liu Silin succeed.

42
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:25,000
Do you know how much effort I've put in

43
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:26,920
to reach this position?

44
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:35,140
It doesn't matter.

45
00:04:36,080 --> 00:04:37,800
You won't need to know anyway.

46
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,280
Because,

47
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:42,280
today,

48
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,440
you're going to die.

49
