but has gotten worse and worse.

54
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:09,240
But,

55
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:14,520
is all this my fault?

56
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,680
Is it my fault?

57
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:25,960
Blame yourself.

58
00:05:27,840 --> 00:05:29,680
It's your own favoritism.

59
00:05:31,840 --> 00:05:33,570
You deserve this retribution.

60
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:51,520
Master.

61
00:06:52,080 --> 00:06:53,240
Where is the young master?

62
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:57,500
