63
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,960
Brother.

64
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,280
Brother.

65
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:15,280
Father has been gone for over a month now.

66
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:17,680
Brother, you need to pull yourself together.

67
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:19,960
The Liu family has so many affairs waiting to be managed.

68
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:23,680
I can't handle everything alone.

69
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:33,280
Do you know what the elders in the family are saying about you?

70
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:34,480
What are they saying?

71
00:07:36,840 --> 00:07:38,570
Never mind. It's not pleasant.

72
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,120
I'd better not say it.

73
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:41,240
Tell me.

74
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,280
What can't you say?

75
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:49,120
They all say the master raised a useless son.

76
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:50,840
A coward.

77
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:53,560
Who only causes trouble when he's not having fits.

78
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:56,840
The master was probably angered to death by him.

79
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,840
Say that again.

80
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:03,200
I said I wouldn't tell you, but you insisted.

81
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:04,240
I told you.

82
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:07,080
Now you're upset and can't accept it.

83
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:12,840
Let me tell you.

84
00:08:13,840 --> 00:08:16,500
Father's death must not be as simple as it seems.

85
00:08:16,840 --> 00:08:19,240
I will find out the truth about everything.

86
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:20,280
Brother.

87
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:22,840
