Young Master Liu manages everything in the Liu family. You're extremely busy.

98
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:18,280
How do you have time to come here?

99
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:20,600
Yiyu, I came specifically to see you.

100
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,050
Are you feeling better?

101
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:24,080
Please don't trouble yourself worrying about me, Young Master.

102
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:24,960
Yiyu.

103
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:26,880
I've finally made it.

104
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:30,130
Now I'm in charge of everything in the Liu household.

105
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:32,900
Do you remember the promise I made to you?

106
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:34,840
Promise.

107
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:38,520
I promised you.

108
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:41,700
Once I take control of the Liu family.

109
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:43,400
