118
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,200
Liu Sinan.

119
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:11,560
Although you're now the head of the Liu family,

120
00:10:12,040 --> 00:10:14,160
Silin is still your elder brother.

121
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:16,480
